Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fizzikgames.fizlib.util.pathfinding.Node

    public class Node
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Node>
    A node is a point in space that has its own coordinates, and can be used to denote points in both 2d and 3d space.
